Personal Notes: The graphics were great, the gameplay was tight, and there was fun additions like glory kills. The guns were all well designed but I felt there was only one good mod for each gun, with the exception of one or two. The main problem was the story. The setting and background information was really good but it was a bare bones story. It started to get old just shooting things for the sake of shooting them. I would be interested in seeing where the story goes for a sequel.
